</paragraph>
<paragraph id="725E36EC249BBDC2FF66DB8B1F8CA50B" blockId="133.[151,1437,437,1584]" pageId="133" pageNumber="134">
<emphasis id="4095EAFE249BBDC2FF66DB8B1AFCA6E2" bold="true" box="[198,451,1481,1507]" pageId="133" pageNumber="134">Taxonomic notes:—</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="B5E14D6F249BBDC2FE63DB8B19CEA6E2" authorityName="Henderson" authorityYear="2011" box="[451,753,1481,1507]" class="Liliopsida" family="Arecaceae" genus="Geonoma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Arecales" pageId="133" pageNumber="134" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sanmartinensis">
<emphasis id="4095EAFE249BBDC2FE63DB8B19CEA6E2" box="[451,753,1481,1507]" italics="true" pageId="133" pageNumber="134">Geonoma sanmartinensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
appears most similar to 
<taxonomicName id="B5E14D6F249BBDC2FB85DB8B1FE8A6E2" authorityName="Martius" authorityYear="1843" box="[1061,1239,1481,1507]" class="Liliopsida" family="Arecaceae" genus="Geonoma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Arecales" pageId="133" pageNumber="134" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="brongniartii">
<emphasis id="4095EAFE249BBDC2FB85DB8B1FE8A6E2" box="[1061,1239,1481,1507]" italics="true" pageId="133" pageNumber="134">G. brongniartii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. It differs in its fruits which are bumpy from the numerous, subepidermal, tangential, short fibers present.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="725E36EC249BBDC2FF66D8541E5EA531" blockId="133.[151,1437,437,1584]" box="[198,1377,1558,1584]" pageId="133" pageNumber="134">
<emphasis id="4095EAFE249BBDC2FF66D8541ACBA531" bold="true" box="[198,500,1558,1584]" pageId="133" pageNumber="134">Subspecific variation:—</emphasis>
No trait varies within this species, nor is there any geographic disjunction.
</paragraph>
